rows.label: qst001005_msg001
rows.name:
I'm glad everyone is
safe. What a relief.

rows.label: qst001005_msg002
rows.name:
From now on, an adult should
go with them so they can
handle any monster attacks.

rows.label: qst001005_msg003
rows.name:
...Well, I'll discuss that with
Yuu-san. You guys really saved us.

rows.label: qst001005_msg005
rows.name:
It's not much, but it's a token of
our gratitude for what you did.

rows.label: qst001005_msg006
rows.name:
We should be the ones thanking you.
You were a great help, thanks!
